WEBVTT

02:43.622 --> 02:46.667
You know the rule.
When you drive...

02:46.709 --> 02:47.668
I get the radio.

02:47.710 --> 02:49.879
I'm not driving yet.

03:51.774 --> 03:54.151
Can you hold it?

04:08.082 --> 04:11.794
It's okay, honey, just go.

09:11.343 --> 09:13.053
Change the music.

10:19.494 --> 10:21.496
Hurry, hurry! Quickly!

10:21.538 --> 10:22.497
Everyone out!

10:22.539 --> 10:23.957
You only have 15 minutes.

10:23.999 --> 10:25.625
Next stop is the coast.

10:29.921 --> 10:32.716
Bathrooms are over there.

11:05.332 --> 11:06.541
Come on, honey.

11:07.667 --> 11:08.668
Go here.

11:26.228 --> 11:27.979
I can do it myself.

11:28.021 --> 11:29.439
Okay, dear.

11:51.670 --> 11:53.296
This one's for women only.

11:53.338 --> 11:54.881
Get out of the way!

12:02.222 --> 12:04.933
-What are you doing in here?
-Out!

12:04.975 --> 12:06.852
-Shame on you!
-Get out!

12:06.893 --> 12:09.646
Come on, everyone out!

12:09.688 --> 12:10.814
Out!

12:23.827 --> 12:25.745
Hurry! Hurry!

24:57.955 --> 24:59.415
My feet hurt.

24:59.457 --> 25:01.000
Mine, too, honey...

25:01.042 --> 25:03.669
but we have to keep walking.

25:05.588 --> 25:07.256
She's tired.

25:09.175 --> 25:12.470
We have to get to the coast
before dark.

25:12.511 --> 25:14.680
Please,
just a few kilometers left.

25:14.722 --> 25:17.016
You said that already.
How do you know?

25:17.058 --> 25:20.394
When we get to the boats...

25:20.436 --> 25:22.730
our problems will be over.

25:28.027 --> 25:29.487
I wish Dad were here.

25:29.528 --> 25:30.696
He'd keep us safe.

25:32.114 --> 25:33.574
Your father?

25:34.700 --> 25:36.369
I'm keeping us safe now!

25:36.410 --> 25:38.913
You think this is hard?

25:38.955 --> 25:42.166
You have no idea what hard is!

25:42.208 --> 25:43.793
One day when you're older...

25:43.834 --> 25:46.295
you'll realize
what I saved you from!

25:46.337 --> 25:49.298
Now, come on! Let's go! Walk!

38:48.368 --> 38:49.995
Yes, Yazid.

38:50.037 --> 38:52.664
I found them at a refugee camp
on a beach in Turkey.

38:54.416 --> 38:56.626
What do you want me to do?

38:58.211 --> 39:00.130
Bring my daughers home.

39:01.173 --> 39:02.215
And your wife?

39:09.806 --> 39:10.807
Sheikh?

39:15.437 --> 39:17.773
Don't let them see.

39:19.316 --> 39:20.358
Yes, Sheikh.

40:17.124 --> 40:18.708
I need to see your boss.

41:44.461 --> 41:45.503
Put down the fucking guns!

41:45.545 --> 41:48.173
What the fuck is going on here?

41:48.215 --> 41:49.299
Tell them to put
their guns down!

41:59.893 --> 42:01.811
Do you know
who you're fucking with?

42:01.853 --> 42:03.980
You know who my family is?

42:04.022 --> 42:05.273
Of course.

42:05.315 --> 42:07.734
I need this woman and her kids.

42:07.776 --> 42:09.569
But he's paid me already.

42:09.611 --> 42:11.363
I can't go back on my word.

42:15.533 --> 42:18.745
You'll offend my family
over a deal with a stranger?

42:18.787 --> 42:20.789
Don't fuck me for petty cash.

42:22.082 --> 42:24.918
If I leave here
without what I came for...

42:24.960 --> 42:27.212
I won't forget it.

43:56.134 --> 43:58.636
No! You can't!

44:00.221 --> 44:01.765
Help me!

45:09.290 --> 45:11.668
Come with us.
We'll get you somewhere safe.
